WEBVTT

00:00:01.169 --> 00:00:07.169
Each year, Jehovah's Witnesses hold conventions around the world in hundreds of languages.

00:00:07.169 --> 00:00:16.910
Those in attendance learn how the Bible can benefit them in practical ways.

00:00:20.859 --> 00:00:24.859
Our three-day conventions include Bible-based talks.

00:00:24.859 --> 00:00:28.859
What a joy it is going to be when death will be no more.

00:00:28.859 --> 00:00:31.859
And move forever and ever.

00:00:31.859 --> 00:00:38.859
Interviews and dramatic reenactments.

00:00:38.859 --> 00:00:49.240
All sessions are open to the public and attendance is free.

00:00:49.240 --> 00:00:53.240
Common sea for yourself by millions attend each year.

00:00:53.240 --> 00:00:56.240
To learn about the next convention to be held near you,

00:00:56.240 --> 00:01:01.240
ask one of Jehovah's Witnesses for more information or visit jw.org.

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:04.239
Click about us, then conventions.
